00:01:37.710 --> 00:01:38.960
moved in with us.

00:01:38.960 --> 00:01:42.040
I suffered from severe pain in the abdomen
and legs.

00:01:42.040 --> 00:01:47.189
Home remedies did not help, and the village
pharmacy did not have the necessary medicines.

00:01:47.189 --> 00:01:52.310
In 1961, my mother and I died of illness and
were buried in our native village.

00:01:52.310 --> 00:01:56.759
I always listened to my heart and it brought
me lots of harmony and beautiful thoughts.

00:01:56.759 --> 00:02:00.770
I wanted to share my worldview with everyone
else through my brushes and eyes.

00:02:00.770 --> 00:02:03.159
I hope we can all see the true charm of our
lives.

